Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • Order
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Order
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Stores all important information of an order created for a customer. This class stores the ID, date and time of the Order object creation, the Staff object who created the Order, and the details of menu item
    Since:
    2021-11-5
